oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Excerpt from Plantation Party
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Excerpt from a broadcast of the Plantation Party, with performances by Louise Massey & The Westerners, the Duke Of Paducah, Curt Massey, Michael Stewart, and the Plantation Choir.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Duke Of Paducah; George Barnes; Curt Massey; Louise Massey & The Westerners; Michael Stewart; Plantation Choir
